OL,7,FA man described as 'paranoid and
OL,8,Fcontrolling' has been jailed after
OL,9,Fcarrying out a sustained and violent
OL,10,Fattack on his partner who believed his
OL,11,Fthreats that she was going to 'die
OL,12,Fthat day'.
OL,14,FHassan Hussain, 26 from Northside Road
OL,15,Fin assaulted the woman over several
OL,16,Fhours, strangling her a number of
OL,17,Ftimes until her eyes were bulging and
OL,18,Fshe couldn't breathe.
