OL,7,FShe was left fearing for her life as
OL,8,Fher violent boyfriend told her: "This
OL,9,Fis the day I'm going to kill you."
OL,10,FBradford Crown Court heard the woman
OL,11,Fhad been in a relationship with
OL,12,FHussain for just nine months when he
OL,13,Fstarted trying to control her through
OL,14,Fhis 'barbaric use of violence'.
OL,15,FHussain first attacked his then-
OL,16,Fpartner on May 9 2023 punching her in
OL,17,Fthe face, grabbing her, and throwing
OL,18,Fher onto a bed. He then strangled her
OL,19,Ffor the first of a number of times.
OL,20,FJust over three weeks later, Hussain
OL,21,Fturned violent again when the woman
OL,22,F"wouldn't let him go through her
OL,23,Fphone".
